{"type": "article", "id": 8765, "title": "「 A’  设计大奖赛」之 Netatmo 家用监控摄像头", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-22T07:28:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235023TvB8QYSo6CpRmAEN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t全世界有大量的儿童一天之内需要度过一段一个人待在家里面的时光，为了保障孩子的安全，让家长放心，Netatmo 推出了这一款家用的监控摄像头，可以通过手机应用，获得全天候的监控视频。这款摄像头具有 130 度的广角以及红外检测系统。摄像头可以进行脸部识别，当扫描到有未经许可的人经过，会自动向使用者发出警告，并提供报警选项。<a href=\"https://competition.adesignaward.com/design.php?ID=38816\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235021YIFuPMQgaGJ5SwUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235021z9GVDvayI5bPmxLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235022pnxNwiaQ6eVKJr52.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.76296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350220uWlfmgsYHkGpdC4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235023ohzaROtxSXiPQLWD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}